items.title: Professor-TA Training Course
items.description:
The purpose of this training course is to give the residential professor, TA, and/or campus Registrar the basic tools needed to build out a residential course in Canvas. Canvas Training Videos and Guides will be made accessible to walk through the various functionalities available within Canvas.
Discussion forums will be available for interaction with the Canvas admin, and other professors and TAs for best practice ideas and to ask questions.
Conferences will be available for video conferencing for group training as needed or upon request.
